text: TarbinskiellusGorochov AV (1983) Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie 62(2): 320. is a genus of crickets in the family Gryllidae and tribe Gryllini. Species can be found in Asia.Orthoptera Species File (Version 5.0/5.0: retrieved 26 August 2019) == Species == Tarbinskiellus includes the following species: *Tarbinskiellus neotropicus Gorochov, 2001 *Tarbinskiellus orientalis Fabricius, 1775 *Tarbinskiellus portentosus Lichtenstein, 1796 \- type species (as Acheta portentosa Lichtenstein AAH) *Tarbinskiellus terrificus Walker, 1869 == References == == External links== * * Category:Ensifera genera Category:Gryllinae Category:Orthoptera of Asia
title: Tarbinskiellus
